<plot>"BEFORE AND AFTER 22/12/1989" is a story about two encounters between two intellectuals and two members of the secret police. The action begins in a Sunday afternoon, in the summer of 1989. There are the last days of the communist regime, when the intellectuals as well as the members of the secret police are tired of showing the tough characters that made of them true symbols of the resistance, respective the oppression.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?263734</url></doc>
